    "The GPT model is a state-of-the-art DL model developed by OpenAI for natural language processing and understanding 48.",
    "The model is grounded in the Transformer architecture 49, renowned for its self-attention mechanism that empowers the model to dynamically weigh and focus on relevant input tokens, thus efficiently capturing long-range dependencies within a sequence.",
